OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775178189
OL,3,CNASA to launch Artemis II in first
OL,4,Chuman Moon mission since 1972
OL,6,FNASA's Artemis II mission will launch
OL,7,Fthis evening, humanity's first flight
OL,8,Fto the moon since 1972.
OL,10,FThe launch is scheduled for 23:24pm
OL,11,FBritish Summer Time (18:24 EDT) from
OL,12,Fthe Kennedy Space Centre in Florida,
OL,13,Fwith the countdown clock scheduled
OL,14,Fsince Monday.
OL,16,FAfter weeks of fuel leaks and other
OL,17,Fissues, things seem to be going NASA's
OL,18,Fway as they proceed toward launch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
