OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775178189
OL,3,CNASA to launch Artemis II in first
OL,4,Chuman Moon mission since 1972
OL,6,FOfficials reported moon rocket was
OL,7,Fdoing well on the pad, and the weather
OL,8,Flooked promising, with forecasters
OL,9,Fputting the odds of favourable
OL,10,Fconditions at 80%.
OL,12,F"Everybody's pretty excited and
OL,13,Funderstands the significance of this
OL,14,Flaunch," said senior test director
OL,15,FJeff Spaulding.
