OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775178189
OL,3,CNASA to launch Artemis II in first
OL,4,Chuman Moon mission since 1972
OL,6,FThe mission, which has cost $93bn
OL,7,F(around #70bn) so far, will send four
OL,8,Fastronauts on a lunar fly-around,
OL,9,Fmeaning they will hurtle several
OL,10,Fthousand miles beyond the moon, make a
OL,11,FU-turn and then come straight back, in
OL,12,Fa mission lasting ten days.
OL,14,FThe Artemis astronauts are Commander
OL,15,FReid Wiseman, Pilot Victor Glover, and
OL,16,FMission specialists Christina Koch,
OL,17,Fand Jeremy Hansen, who between them
OL,18,Fwill make history as the first person
OL,19,Fof colour, first woman, and first non-
OL,20,FAmerican on the moon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
