FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775178189
OL,3,CNASA to launch Artemis II in first
OL,4,Chuman Moon mission since 1972
OL,6,FThe test flight is part of NASA's
OL,7,Flonger term plans, which hope to send
OL,8,Fmore people to walk on the moon, after
OL,9,Fa number of practice missions.
OL,11,FThe Artemis II crew may behold never-
OL,12,Fbefore-seen regions of the lunar far
OL,13,Fside ` with the moon appearing the
OL,14,Fsize of a basketball at arm's length
OL,15,Fduring the closest part of the roughly
OL,16,Fsix-hour flyby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
