FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775178189
OL,3,CNASA to launch Artemis II in first
OL,4,Chuman Moon mission since 1972
OL,6,FIn preparation, the crew have been
OL,7,Flooking at maps and satellite images
OL,8,Fof the lunar far side and will carry
OL,9,Flatest smartphones and professional
OL,10,Fcamera on the mission to take a number
OL,11,Fof images.
OL,13,FTheir lunar mentor NASA geologist
OL,14,FKelsey Young, who will monitor the
OL,15,Fflyby from Mission Control in Houston,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The moon is like such a
OL,17,Funifying thing. What we're doing with
OL,18,Fthis mission is going to bring that a
OL,19,Flittle closer to everybody around the
OL,20,Fworld."
