OL,3,CNASA to launch Artemis II in first
OL,4,Chuman Moon mission since 1972
OL,6,FLaunch day was originally planned for
OL,7,FFebruary, but was delayed due to bad
OL,8,Fweather, and later due to a liquid
OL,9,Fhydrogen leak.
